ally for thick, resistant hormonal hair</strong> — not for fine leg hair.</li>\n    <li><strong>3-phase system with pre-treatment:</strong> standard creams have no preparation phase. Dermelia opens the hair structure before acting.</li>\n    <li><strong>Clinical concentration of active ingredients:</strong> sufficient to dissolve dense hormonal hair, not just fine strands.</li>\n    <li><strong>Soothing post-treatment formula:</strong> no standard cream includes a skin recovery phase.</li>\n    <li><strong>Designed for continuous use that improves over time</strong> — not for one-off removal.</li>\n  </ul>\n\n  <p>The difference is felt from the first application. And it shows in the weeks that follow — not because Dermelia performs \"magic,\" but because it's the first method that stops feeding the problem instead of making it worse.</p>\n\n  <hr class=\"section-divider\">\n\n  <div class=\"cta-section\">\n    <div class=\"guarantee-badge\">NO RISK — 60-DAY GUARANTEE</div>\n    <h2>Break the trauma cycle.<br>Start improving instead of getting worse.</h2>\n    <p>Complete Trilogy Kit — 3 natural phases for hormonal hair<br>\n    Polycystic ovary • Menopause • Hormonal fluctuations • Post-pregnancy</p>\n    <img class=\"full-width\" src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0921/5538/0039/files/ChatGPT_Image_11_mag_2026_12_38_31.png?v=1778524336\" alt=\"Dermelia Kit Trilogy\" style=\"max-width:400px; margin: 0 auto 24px; display:block;\">\n    <a href=\"/products/kit-depilazione\" class=\"cta-btn\">Try Dermelia risk-free →</a>\n    <div class=\"cta-trust\">\n      <span>✓ 60-day money-back guarantee</span>\n      <span>✓ Fast shipping</span>\n      <span>✓ Dermatologically tested</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <hr class=\"section-divider\">\n\n  <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>\n\n  <details class=\"faq-item\">\n    <summary>Will it work for me?</summary>\n    <ul>\n      <li>Suitable for thick and fine hair.</li>\n      <li>Effective for excessive and hormonal h